snippet.title: Aniquilation - (PS4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, PC)
snippet.description:
Aniquilation is a Twin stick action-shooter game where your objective is to destroy all the buildings and enemies that are destroying the planets of your galaxy.
Play in multiplayer player split-screen couch-coop mode through story mode, or compete with your friends in the 4 PVP VS modes!
